title:  "Did these fans go too far ? Boca, Corinthians and the 2022 Copa Libertadores"
---
A few weeks ago, in the early morning before the 2022 Copa Libertadores Round of 16, Boca fanatics created an incredible ruckus right in front of the Hotel Madero, where opposition side Corinthians were staying. 
Fanatics from sides across South America often try to "tip the scales" of a match - the remarkable footage from the incident at the Hotel Madero, shows how far passion drives football fans.
This video tells the whole story.
This article, tells the story in greater detail](link.com)

